org/resource/Gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He assured the ambassador that the team would represent Nigeria with pride and distinction throughout the competition.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999978554115, \"rank\": 2.1201255870143145e-09, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asuquo also highlighted the significance of the ambassador's provision of accommodations, noting that it greatly alleviates the logistical challenges faced by the team and allows them to focus on their performance.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ambassador's gesture has been a source of great encouragement for the Nigerian gymnasts, reinforcing their determination to excel and bring honour to their country.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1493, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.9963436034200714, \"rank\": 0.0036698148477676057, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team's gratitude and commitment to representing Nigeria well underscores the importance of such supportive diplomatic relationships in the realm of international sports.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join Daily Trust WhatsApp Community For Quick Access To News and Happenings Around You.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": []}]}"